# Git Remote Policy

- Never push to the `dreamtreelab` GitHub organization. That is not our repo.
- The only valid remote is `origin` pointing to `github.com/jlin3/substream-sdk`.
- Before any `git push`, verify `git remote -v` shows `jlin3` in the URL.
- If a `dreamtreelab` remote exists, remove it immediately with `git remote remove <name>`.
